1
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:12,361
I mean it, Nano.

2
00:00:12,461 --> 00:00:14,711
I saw her with my own eyes.

3
00:00:14,884 --> 00:00:18,735
Maheen was behind the white-bearded man.

4
00:00:20,265 --> 00:00:22,358
For a moment, I felt

5
00:00:22,655 --> 00:00:25,504
Like my world had been upended.

6
00:00:27,014 --> 00:00:29,235
Until... She approached me.

7
00:00:31,980 --> 00:00:33,488
Maheen?

8
00:00:34,108 --> 00:00:35,628
Of course.

9
00:00:36,048 --> 00:00:37,428
Maheen.

10
00:00:39,408 --> 00:00:40,938
She said,

11
00:00:41,579 --> 00:00:44,410
'The painter remembers his painting, Gulrez',

12
00:00:45,121 --> 00:00:48,222
'But not the other way around'.

13
00:00:48,892 --> 00:00:51,751
'The painting but looks for an art gallery'

14
00:00:51,783 --> 00:00:54,823
'That would adorn its ornamented wall with her beauty'.

15
00:00:58,080 --> 00:00:59,011
So

16
00:00:59,011 --> 00:01:00,561
You

17
00:01:02,990 --> 00:01:05,559
Are here to tell me

18
00:01:09,211 --> 00:01:10,800
That you

19
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:15,998
Aren't gonna marry Maheen?

20
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:28,689
Don't mistake me for one of your English roses,

21
00:01:28,689 --> 00:01:31,862
Who'd fall for the hollow words of a London tramp!

22
00:01:33,850 --> 00:01:35,638
If I talk nicely to you,

23
00:01:35,638 --> 00:01:38,818
Just know it's my love for Uncle Mashood!

24
00:01:38,898 --> 00:01:41,444
As for you, I loathe you so much

25
00:01:41,444 --> 00:01:44,019
I'd spit in your face any day!

26
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:47,231
But <i>you</i>!

27
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:51,588
You dare say you want to marry Maheen Aurangzeb?

28
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:54,150
D'you think Your Highness is at a departmental store?

29
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:57,921
D'you think you can pull out your riches and buy everything under the sun?

30
00:02:04,010 --> 00:02:05,848
Have some shame!

31
00:02:05,876 --> 00:02:07,940
You're friends with God-knows-how-many girls!

32
00:02:07,940 --> 00:02:10,428
And now, you've got your eyes on <i>me</i>!

33
00:02:22,010 --> 00:02:24,638
Your Royal Highness would do well to remember

34
00:02:24,638 --> 00:02:27,908
I won't think twice before chopping those filthy hands off!

35
00:02:29,128 --> 00:02:30,448
Stop it, Maheen!

36
00:02:30,448 --> 00:02:32,139
Don't stop me, Aunt.

37
00:02:32,219 --> 00:02:33,669
It's best for him

38
00:02:33,669 --> 00:02:37,695
If he packed his bags and jetted off to London before this instant!

39
00:02:38,810 --> 00:02:41,619
You can't stay here!

40
00:02:41,709 --> 00:02:43,510
So get going!

41
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,428
And aye,

42
00:02:48,564 --> 00:02:51,414
If you dared say so much as my name,

43
00:02:51,505 --> 00:02:53,240
I'd ruin you!

44
00:02:53,240 --> 00:03:07,339
♪ <i>Love's testimony is not to be asked of it</i> ♪

45
